Package io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.implementation.listeners

Class BlockPhysicsListener

java.lang.Object
io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.implementation.listeners.BlockPhysicsListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
Listener
public class BlockPhysicsListener extends Object implements Listener
This Listener is responsible for listening to any physics-based events, such as EntityChangeBlockEvent or a BlockPistonEvent. This ensures that a Piston cannot be abused to break Slimefun blocks.
Author:
VoidAngel, Poslovitch, TheBusyBiscuit, AccelShark
